<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٠٣٦ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ الْحَنْظَلِيُّ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3447">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ، </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6737">هَمَّامِ بْنِ مُنَبِّهٍ </a>قَالَ: هَذَا مَا حَدَّثَنَا بِهِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ، </a>عَنْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَحْنُ الْآخِرُونَ السَّابِقُونَ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>